## 2ï¸âƒ£ Decorative vertical edge lines

```tsx
<div className="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 mx-auto max-w-5xl">
```

### Breakdown:

| Class                 | Meaning                                                |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| `absolute`            | Positioned **relative to parent** (`relative` wrapper) |
| `inset-0`             | Top, right, bottom, left = `0`                         |
| `mx-auto`             | Center horizontally                                    |
| `max-w-5xl`           | Limits width (prevents full screen stretch)            |
| `z-0`                 | Sends it **behind content**                            |
| `pointer-events-none` | Mouse clicks go **through** it                         |

